1.title: I Need a Plane
1.plot: In order to make a killer music video for G Fella's new song, the crew needs an airplane. Cousin Ralphie and Cousin Anthony "got a guy." Now it's just a matter of getting "him" to lend G his plane. Meantime, the Three Kings tell G he needs to show signs of success or they will cut off his funding.

2.title: Beefin'
2.plot: G Fella's childhood friend, Grizz, posts a viral video putting G on blast. The crew has to decide the best way to respond to his threat without anyone getting hurt.

3.title: Goomahs
3.plot: Ralphie, Anthony, and The Three Kings go to rap school and come back with an idea to write a song and shoot a video about G's "other women." But once his wife hears about it all hell breaks loose and she crashes the video shoot.

4.title: G Is Shot
4.plot: The crew convinces G Fella that the key to fame is getting shot. It's a great idea, until it works... too well.

6.title: Sensitive Italian Male
6.plot: With a potential investor in their label on the line, G Fella and Johnny Thurzday get distracted by their wives involvement in a nude photo shoot.

locations: New York City, New York, USA
imdb.plot outline: G-Thing follows an Italian-American rapper and his larger-than-life family as they try to launch their first "family-style" run hip-hop label: Tracketeering Records. Viewers will get an inside look at G Fella, along with his unrestrained and crazy relatives, as they do everything they can to achieve musical stardom.
